project_descr: Global Gender Equality supported through 10 Senior Gender Advisers to augment leadership and technical capacity of 10 crisis countries to deliver better for women and girls in post-conflict contexts.

outputs.output_descr: Advancing Gender Equality and Women Empowerment in ten targeted countries (Burundi, Haiti, Iraq, Kosovo, Liberia, Nepal, Papua New Guinea, Sierra Leone, South Sudan and Timor-Leste).
